## III. Layout Selection Rules

### Automatic Layout Detection

```
IF content ends with "?" → question
IF content has quotation marks + name → quote
IF content references image/diagram → image
IF content is < 8 words → title
IF content has bullet points → content
DEFAULT → content
```

### Position-Based Rules

| Position | Required Layout | Rationale |
|----------|----------------|-----------|
| First | title | Set context, immediate impact |
| Last | title OR content | Conclusion or CTA |
| After 2+ content | question OR image | Visual variety |

### Variety Enforcement

**Never allow:**
- 3+ consecutive `content` slides
- 2+ consecutive `title` slides
- `question` immediately after `question`

**Inject variety:**
- After 2 content slides, suggest question or image
- Alternate bullet-heavy and minimal slides

