## VI. Error Prevention

### Common Mistakes to Avoid

| Error | Fix |
|-------|-----|
| Too many bullets (>5) | Split into multiple slides |
| Full sentences in bullets | Convert to fragments |
| Missing heading | Always add heading |
| Tiny text (<28px) | Increase to minimum |
| No logo | Add to every slide |
| Same layout 3x | Inject variety |

### Content Red Flags

**Trigger manual review if:**
- Input exceeds 300 words
- More than 3 frameworks mentioned
- Image references without URLs
- Mixed languages without clear pattern

